OL,6,FJobs in the City's financial services
OL,7,Fsector have "plummeted" over the past
OL,8,Fyear amid mounting challenges,
OL,9,Faccording to a new report.
OL,11,FServices firm Morgan McKinley said its
OL,12,Fstudy suggested there had been an 18%
OL,13,Freduction in the final few months of
OL,14,Flast year and a 12% annual decline.
OL,16,FDirector Mark Astbury said: "The
OL,17,Ffinancial services sector in London
OL,18,Fsuffered a contraction in 2024, with
OL,19,Fjob availability plummeting.
